      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Pascal Georges</b>\n</p><p><b>Pascal Georges</b><br />\na French software developer who worked on <a href=\"/SCID\" title=\"SCID\">Shane's Chess Information Database</a>, SCID from December 2006 to January 2010. \nAmongst other things, he added <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Free_Internet_Chess_Server&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Free Internet Chess Server (page does not exist)\">FICS</a> and <a href=\"/Novag_Citrine\" title=\"Novag Citrine\">Novag Citrine</a> support, docking modes, \ntraining features, and ported SCID to the <a href=\"/index.php?title=Pocket_PC&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Pocket PC (page does not exist)\">Pocket PC</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2007_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2007 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pascal_Georges&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2007_...\">2007 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pascal_Georges&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2007 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/SnJ7z4skk90/GzKPI5sdIdgJ\">Features added to Scid</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, January 02, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/ZYpY2aF7mq8/d_eR1762lroJ\">Scid 3.6.4 released (chess database)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, February 24, 2007 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.avlerchess.com/chess-computer/Scid_366_released_chess_database_179456.html\">Scid 3.6.6 released (chess database)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.avlerchess.com/\">Avler Chess</a>, March 07, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=13060\">Patch proposal for Toga</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 12, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Toga\" title=\"Toga\">Toga</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=13095\">Scid 3.6.11 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 13, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=14341\">Scid for Pocket PC - alpha release available</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 07, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=15470\">Novag Citrine and Scid</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 31, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Novag_Citrine\" title=\"Novag Citrine\">Novag Citrine</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/I-J53bggxm8/YJGioTFWSHUJ\">Why Scid should stay alive [Re: Statistical significance of score differences - new release ofChessDB]</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, August 22, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=16459\">Scid for Pocket PC with Toga and Glaurung</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 14, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Toga\" title=\"Toga\">Toga</a>, <a href=\"/Glaurung\" title=\"Glaurung\">Glaurung</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=17001\">Scid Pocket 0.21 released (with Phalanx)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 07, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Phalanx\" title=\"Phalanx\">Phalanx</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2008</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=18781\">How to interface Novag Citrine with PC</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 06, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Novag_Citrine\" title=\"Novag Citrine\">Novag Citrine</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=19129\">New version of Scid Pocket</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 22, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=21001\">Elo rating of chess engines on Pocket PC</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 04, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=22935\">Intel Atom processor and nodes per second</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 12, 2008</li></ul>\n<p><b>2009</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=29621\">Scid 4.0 (chess database and training software)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 02, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=31228\">Bit Scan (equivalent to ASM instructions bsr and bsf)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 24, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/BitScan\" title=\"BitScan\">BitScan</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=31230\">Scid Pocket v4 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 24, 2009</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pascal_Georges&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=31429\">Scid 4.1 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 02, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=31608\">Handling UCI protocol and Stockfish / Glaurung behavior</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 10, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a>, <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a>, <a href=\"/Glaurung\" title=\"Glaurung\">Glaurung</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=31847\">Scid 4.2 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pascal Georges</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 19, 2010</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pascal_Georges&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sourceforge.net/p/scid/wiki/ScidAuthors/\">Scid / Wiki / ScidAuthors</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://scid.sourceforge.net/author.html\">Scid: A Free Chess Database App - Author</a>\t</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a